entry.title: DashboardPack/architectui-html-theme-free
entry.summary: ArchitectUI Dashboard Free is lightweight and comes packed with the minimal set of components to get you started. If you have a simple application, it’s the perfect solution for you. It’s built on top of Bootstrap 5 and features a scalable architecture just like it’s wiser, older sibling – ArchitectUI HTML Pro theme.
